## Platform API

The platform exposes **75+ RESTful endpoints** across 13 route modules. All endpoints are prefixed with `/api/v1/` and documented via OpenAPI at `/docs`.

### Endpoint Summary

| Category              | Endpoints | Highlights                                                   |
| --------------------- | --------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Auth**              | 8         | Register, login, JWT + refresh rotation, password reset      |
| **Company & Data**    | 7         | Company CRUD, data upload with pagination                    |
| **Carbon Estimation** | 6         | Local/subnet estimation, reports, dashboard, CSV/JSON export |
| **AI Enhancement**    | 4         | Text parsing, prediction, audit trail, recommendations       |
| **Questionnaires**    | 10        | Upload, AI extraction, templates, PDF export                 |
| **Scenarios**         | 5         | What-if scenario builder with compute                        |
| **Supply Chain**      | 6         | Supplier linking, Scope 3 propagation                        |
| **Compliance**        | 1         | GHG Protocol / CDP / TCFD / SBTi reports                     |
| **Billing**           | 5         | Subscription management, credits, plans                      |
| **Alerts**            | 3         | Emission threshold alerts, acknowledgement                   |
| **Marketplace**       | 5         | Anonymized data listings, credit-based purchase              |
| **Webhooks**          | 5         | HMAC-signed webhooks, delivery logs                          |
| **Audit & Health**    | 2         | Audit logs, health check                                     |

> For the complete endpoint reference with request/response examples, see [API.md](../API.md).

## Data Models

The platform uses **16 SQLAlchemy models** with full async support, soft deletes, and CHECK constraints.

| Model                     | Description                                                           |
| ------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Company**               | Organization profile (industry, region, revenue, employees)           |
| **User**                  | Authenticated member (email, bcrypt password, role: admin/member)     |
| **DataUpload**            | Raw operational data (year, JSON `provided_data`)                     |
| **EmissionReport**        | Calculated emissions (S1/S2/S3, breakdown, confidence, miner scores)  |
| **SupplyChainLink**       | Buyer↔supplier relationship (spend, category, verification status)    |
| **Webhook**               | HTTP callback endpoint (URL, event types, HMAC secret)                |
| **WebhookDelivery**       | Delivery log (status code, duration, retry info)                      |
| **AuditLog**              | Action audit trail (user, action, resource type/id)                   |
| **Questionnaire**         | Uploaded document (PDF/DOCX/XLSX/CSV, extraction status)              |
| **QuestionnaireQuestion** | Extracted question with AI draft + human-reviewed answer              |
| **Scenario**              | What-if analysis (parameters, base report, computed results)          |
| **Subscription**          | Company plan tier (free/pro/enterprise, billing status)               |
| **CreditLedger**          | Credit transaction log (grants, deductions, running balance)          |
| **Alert**                 | Automated alert (emission increase, confidence drop, target exceeded) |
| **DataListing**           | Marketplace listing (anonymized data, price in credits)               |
| **DataPurchase**          | Marketplace purchase transaction record                               |

> For database schema relationships and architecture details, see [ARCHITECTURE.md](../ARCHITECTURE.md).

